01:02:14.147 --> 01:02:18.484
- [Beeping]
- They shoot the shit out
of this area all the time.

482
01:02:18.568 --> 01:02:21.237
All the flights out of LAX
avoid it like the plague.

483
01:02:21.321 --> 01:02:24.240
- Can you go below radar?
- Not marine radar.

484
01:02:24.324 --> 01:02:27.576
Maybe if I get us close enough to the water.
the waves can camouflage us.

485
01:02:27.661 --> 01:02:30.579
- Go down.
- Oh. Okay.

486
01:02:30.664 --> 01:02:32.873
- Do it.
- Hang on.

487
01:02:39.965 --> 01:02:43.217
[Beeping]

488
01:02:43.301 --> 01:02:45.636
[Long Beep]

489
01:02:46.638 --> 01:02:48.681
We lost them. sir.

490
01:03:09.369 --> 01:03:13.664
[Speaking Spanish]

491
01:03:23.800 --> 01:03:25.718
Slitting
a little girl's throat...

492
01:03:25.802 --> 01:03:28.220
is like cutting
warm butter.

493
01:03:29.556 --> 01:03:31.807
Put the knife away...

494
01:03:31.892 --> 01:03:33.934
and shut your mouth.

495
01:03:41.401 --> 01:03:45.154
I love listening to your little pissant soldiers
trying to talk tough.

496
01:03:46.156 --> 01:03:48.157
They make me laugh.

497
01:03:48.241 --> 01:03:51.076
If Matrix was here.
he'd laugh too.

498
01:03:51.161 --> 01:03:54.663
Mr. Bennett. my soldiers
are patriots.

499
01:03:54.748 --> 01:03:56.707
Your soldiers are nothing.

500
01:03:56.791 --> 01:04:00.336
Matrix and I could kill every one of them
in the blink ofan eye.

501
01:04:00.420 --> 01:04:06.133
- Remember that.
- Are you trying to frighten me?

502
01:04:06.218 --> 01:04:08.511
I don't have to try.

503
01:04:08.595 --> 01:04:13.390
When Matrix finishes the job.
he'll be back for his daughter.

504
01:04:13.475 --> 01:04:19.438
Whether she's alive or dead doesn't matter.
Then he'll be after you.

505
01:04:19.523 --> 01:04:22.900
The only thing
between Matrix and you...

506
01:04:23.902 --> 01:04:25.903
is me.

507
01:04:25.987 --> 01:04:31.158
It is you that is afraid.
Mr. Bennett.

508
01:04:32.452 --> 01:04:35.454
You are afraid of Matrix.

509
01:04:35.539 --> 01:04:39.833
Of course.
I'm smart.

510
01:04:39.918 --> 01:04:42.503
But I have an edge.

511
01:04:42.587 --> 01:04:45.297
I have his daughter.

512
01:04:48.969 --> 01:04:51.887
- Is that it?
- That's the one.

513
01:04:55.976 --> 01:05:00.229
Land here. It's the most
isolated spot we'll find.

514
01:05:00.313 --> 01:05:03.649
Okay. here we go.

515
01:05:49.571 --> 01:05:51.697
Now. you remember the message?

516
01:05:51.781 --> 01:05:56.660
Commando. Kirby. Code Red.
Coordinates. Got it.

517
01:05:56.745 --> 01:05:59.830
Don't break radio silence
until they see me.

518
01:05:59.914 --> 01:06:04.126
- How will I know?
- Because all fucking hell is gonna break loose.

519
01:06:04.210 --> 01:06:07.546
Be careful. Matrix.
Good luck.

520
01:06:07.631 --> 01:06:10.591
Thanks.

521
01:06:48.004 --> 01:06:51.340
[Speaking Spanish]

522
01:08:10.003 --> 01:08:13.046
[Grunting]

523
01:08:55.423 --> 01:08:57.633
[Speaking Spanish]

524
01:09:29.123 --> 01:09:32.125
[Indistinct]

525
01:09:40.176 --> 01:09:45.180
[Ringing]

526
01:09:49.686 --> 01:09:53.897
[Speaking Spanish]

527
01:10:13.877 --> 01:10:15.961
He was not on the plane.

528
01:10:18.631 --> 01:10:21.425
Kill her.

529
01:10:25.305 --> 01:10:28.765
[Groaning]

530
01:10:42.363 --> 01:10:44.698
[Groaning]

531
01:10:44.782 --> 01:10:48.160
- [Speaks Spanish]
- [Groans]

532
01:10:51.539 --> 01:10:54.124
[Speaks Spanish]

533
01:10:54.208 --> 01:10:57.294
- [Alarm Sounds]
- [Screams]

534
01:11:18.066 --> 01:11:20.692
[Explosion]

535
01:11:20.777 --> 01:11:24.446
Welcome back. John.
So glad you could make it.

536
01:11:31.663 --> 01:11:36.083
[Men Chattering. Yelling]

537
01:11:41.965 --> 01:11:44.007
- [Explosion]
- That little...

538
01:11:44.092 --> 01:11:46.468
bitch!

539
01:11:48.554 --> 01:11:50.764
[Roars]

540
01:11:54.310 --> 01:11:57.771
[Yells]

541
01:12:01.609 --> 01:12:04.611
[Men Yelling In Spanish]

542
01:12:15.456 --> 01:12:18.208
[Yelling In Spanish]

543
01:12:40.356 --> 01:12:43.817
Commando.
I say again. Commando.

544
01:12:43.901 --> 01:12:46.319
This is Whiskey Xray 448.

545
01:12:46.404 --> 01:12:50.032
I have an emergency priority message
for a General Franklin Kirby.

546
01:12:50.116 --> 01:12:52.534
I repeat.
General Franklin Kirby.

547
01:12:52.618 --> 01:12:57.706
General. you'd better get out here.
We have your message on the Teletype.

548
01:12:59.042 --> 01:13:01.835
- [Shouts]
- [Gunshots]

549
01:13:35.203 --> 01:13:38.330
[Shouting]

550
01:14:07.902 --> 01:14:09.986
[Shouts]

551
01:14:29.549 --> 01:14:33.009
[Gunshots]

552
01:14:47.066 --> 01:14:49.234
[Groans]

553
01:14:52.321 --> 01:14:54.406
[Grunts]

554
01:14:58.202 --> 01:15:00.745
[Speaking Spanish]

555
01:15:09.255 --> 01:15:12.257
[Speaking Spanish]

556
01:15:14.802 --> 01:15:16.928
[Speaking Spanish]

557
01:15:24.437 --> 01:15:26.479
[Screams]

558
01:15:27.773 --> 01:15:31.234
[Grunting]

559
01:15:44.582 --> 01:15:46.958
[Speaking Spanish]

560
01:16:05.811 --> 01:16:08.188
[Yelling]

561
01:16:30.753 --> 01:16:33.546
[Shouts]

562
01:17:19.760 --> 01:17:22.053
[Groaning]

563
01:17:48.247 --> 01:17:50.749
Jenny!

564
01:17:55.212 --> 01:17:57.505
Jenny?

565
01:17:57.590 --> 01:17:59.758
Jenny!

566
01:18:05.931 --> 01:18:08.141
[Men Shouting In Spanish]

567
01:19:13.332 --> 01:19:15.667
Daddy?

568
01:19:50.161 --> 01:19:52.162
Jenny!

569
01:19:55.332 --> 01:19:57.709
Daddy?

570
01:19:59.211 --> 01:20:01.212
Daddy?

571
01:20:02.631 --> 01:20:06.468
- Jenny!
- Daddy?

572
01:20:06.552 --> 01:20:10.138
- [Screams]
- No. Not Daddy.

573
01:20:10.222 --> 01:20:12.348
Come on!

574
01:20:18.814 --> 01:20:21.774
Daddy. [Screams]

575
01:20:24.236 --> 01:20:29.032
- John! How's your arm?
- Come over and find out.

576
01:20:29.116 --> 01:20:31.910
No. thanks.
I think I'll take a pass.

577
01:20:33.204 --> 01:20:35.413
John. stick your head out.

578
01:20:35.498 --> 01:20:38.041
One shot.
right between the eyes.

579
01:20:38.125 --> 01:20:41.085
I'll make it quick.
just for old times' sake.

580
01:20:41.170 --> 01:20:44.589
Bennett. stop screwing around
and let the girl go.

581
01:20:44.673 --> 01:20:47.717
- It's me that you want. I have only one arm.
- [Laughing]

582
01:20:47.801 --> 01:20:49.802
You can beat me.

583
01:20:49.887 --> 01:20:52.680
Come on. Bennett.

584
01:20:52.765 --> 01:20:55.141
Throw away
that chickenshit gun.

585
01:20:57.603 --> 01:21:02.106
You don't just want to pull a trigger.
Put the knife in me...

586
01:21:02.191 --> 01:21:05.860
and look me in the eye
and see what's going on in there...

587
01:21:05.945 --> 01:21:07.904
when you turn it.

588
01:21:07.988 --> 01:21:10.573
- That's what you want to do. right?
- I can kill you. John.

589
01:21:10.658 --> 01:21:12.575
Come on.
Let the girl go.

590
01:21:12.660 --> 01:21:17.080
It's between you and me. Don't
deprive yourself of some pleasure.

591
01:21:17.164 --> 01:21:20.208
Come on. Bennett.
Let's party.

592
01:21:20.292 --> 01:21:22.585
- I can beat you.
- [Whimpers] No.

593
01:21:22.670 --> 01:21:24.671
I don't need the girl.
[Scoffs]

594
01:21:24.755 --> 01:21:26.714
- I don't need the girl!
- [Squeals]

595
01:21:26.799 --> 01:21:30.260
[Laughs]
I don't need the gun. John.

596
01:21:30.344 --> 01:21:32.762
I can beat you.
[Laughs]

597
01:21:32.846 --> 01:21:34.847
I don't need no gun!

598
01:21:37.351 --> 01:21:40.061
I'm gonna kill you now!

599
01:21:41.355 --> 01:21:45.775
[Screaming]

600
01:21:55.536 --> 01:21:58.538
[Shouts. Laughs]

601
01:21:58.622 --> 01:22:01.666
- Daddy.
- You're getting old. John.

602
01:22:03.294 --> 01:22:06.629
You're getting old.

603
01:22:09.049 --> 01:22:12.510
[Groans]

604
01:22:17.600 --> 01:22:20.143
[Both Grunting]

605
01:23:06.190 --> 01:23:09.734
[Grunting]

606
01:23:31.215 --> 01:23:34.884
[Screaming]

607
01:23:43.018 --> 01:23:46.187
John. I feel good.
just like old times.

608
01:23:47.356 --> 01:23:50.608
What's it feel like
to be a dying man?

609
01:23:50.693 --> 01:23:53.152
- You're a dead man!
- Bullshit!

610
01:24:01.745 --> 01:24:04.997
John. I'm not gonna
shoot you between the eyes.

611
01:24:05.082 --> 01:24:07.792
I'll shoot
you between the balls!

612
01:24:10.254 --> 01:24:13.840
- [Steam Hisses]
- [Gagging]

613
01:24:16.093 --> 01:24:18.886
[Grunting]

614
01:24:22.182 --> 01:24:24.892
Let off some steam.
Bennett.

615
01:24:28.856 --> 01:24:30.857
Daddy.

616
01:25:11.356 --> 01:25:13.441
Move out!

617
01:25:37.341 --> 01:25:40.384
[Indistinct]

618
01:25:48.393 --> 01:25:51.979
- Leave anything for us?
- Just bodies.

619
01:25:52.064 --> 01:25:55.149
I'd just like you to start
up your unit again. John.

620
01:25:55.234 --> 01:25:59.153
- All it would take is your coming back.
- This was the last time.

621
01:26:06.745 --> 01:26:09.497
## [Rock]

622
01:26:09.581 --> 01:26:12.250
Until the next time.

623
01:26:24.721 --> 01:26:26.639
No chance.

624
01:26:26.723 --> 01:26:31.561
## [Man Singing]

625
01:27:15.522 --> 01:27:17.857
## [Continues]

626
01:27:43.133 --> 01:27:45.509
## [Continues]

627
01:28:13.372 --> 01:28:15.748
## [Continues]

628
01:28:40.857 --> 01:28:46.195
## [Guitar Solo]

629
01:29:20.981 --> 01:29:23.232
## [Singing Continues]

630
01:29:49.885 --> 01:29:52.303
## [Continues]

631
